r><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132115815,imgsize-51010.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin truck driver killed in fuel tanker crash in Australia; wife says he was 25 years old]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132079044.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A heartbreaking incident unfolded on Victoria's Princes Freeway, taking the life of 25-year-old Ashwani Sharma, an Indian-origin truck driver. His fuel tanker overturned close to Warragul, leading to major road closures and a hazardous spill. In the wake of this tragedy, Sharma's wife has voiced her sorrow and is seeking community support to cope with the significant emotional and financial burdens following his unexpected demise.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-origin-truck-driver-ashwani-sharma-killed-in-fuel-tanker-crash-in-australia-wife-says-he-was-just-25-years-old/articleshow/132079044.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-origin-truck-driver-ashwani-sharma-killed-in-fuel-tanker-crash-in-australia-wife-says-he-was-just-25-years-old/articleshow/132079044.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-01T17:35:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132114821,imgsize-93720.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[6 Cities that could be buried by lava one day without warning: From Naples in Italy to Pahoa in the US]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132114605.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/6-cities-that-could-be-buried-by-lava-one-day-without-